This file is a placeholder for the system flow diagram.

Recommended diagram content:
- Three boxes: CSCO (red) → GSAI (green) → Ledger (blue)
- Arrows between them showing data flow
- Input arrow from left, Output arrow to right
- Labels on each box with key metrics

For generation:
- Use draw.io / Excalidraw / Mermaid
- Output as PNG at 1200×400px

Mermaid equivalent:
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[AI Input] --> B[CSCO\nConstraint Gate]
    B -- unsafe --> X[❌ REJECTED]
    B -- safe --> C[GSAI\nBounded Score]
    C -- score >= 0.5 --> D[Decision Engine]
    D --> E[Ledger\nImmutable Audit]
    E --> F[✅ Output]
    C -- score < 0.5 --> X
```
